'''''Alaya Deepam''''' ({{Literal translation|The temple lamp}}) is a [[1984 in film|1984]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]]  [[Cinema of India|Indian]] feature film directed by [[C. V. Sridhar]] and produced by K.R.Gangadharan. It stars [[Sujatha (actress)|Sujatha]] and [[Rajesh (actor)|Rajesh]] in the lead roles.<ref>{{cite web|title=Alaya Deepam Vinyl LP Records|url=http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers/36/3/1/1|publisher=musicalaya|accessdate=2014-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424021042/http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers%2F36%2F3%2F1%2F1|archive-date=24 April 2014|dead-url=yes|df=dmy-all}}</ref>

